---
title: Creamy Honey Mustard Pork with Herby Mash & Steamed Veggies
description: Add some flair to your usual meat and three veggies with these sweet honey mustard-glazed pork steaks. Along with a silky herbed mash, it'll be tough deciding what the best part of this quick and easy dish is!

*Keep an eye out...Due to sourcing challenges over the Christmas period, some of the fresh ingredients you receive may be different to what’s pictured. Don’t worry, your recipe will be just as delicious!*
